font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">熱刺</span></span></strong>是一間座落英國倫敦北部托定咸區的職業足球會<br />\n從1882年成立至今已經擁有過百年歷史，現時競逐於英格蘭超級聯賽；<br />\n球會主場為白鹿徑球場，球會的拉丁文格言 &rdquo;<em>Audere est Facere (To Dare Is To Do)</em>&rdquo; 則意謂「<em>敢作敢為</em>」</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/uploadedImages/Shared_Assets/Images/History/Honours/league_champions_1951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tottenhamhotspur.com%2FuploadedImages%2FShared_Assets%2FImages%2FHistory%2FHonours%2Fleague_champions_1951.jpg&h=6a1de3c7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/uploadedImages/Shared_Assets/Images/News_images/SEASON_13-14/Legends/double_team_history730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tottenhamhotspur.com%2FuploadedImages%2FShared_Assets%2FImages%2FNews_images%2FSEASON_13-14%2FLegends%2Fdouble_team_history730.jpg&h=65af9c36&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/uploadedImages/Shared_Assets/Images/History/Year_By_Year/1999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tottenhamhotspur.com%2FuploadedImages%2FShared_Assets%2FImages%2FHistory%2FYear_By_Year%2F1999.jpg&h=466fc807&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/uploadedImages/Shared_Assets/Images/History/Honours/carling_cup_winners_2008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tottenhamhotspur.com%2FuploadedImages%2FShared_Assets%2FImages%2FHistory%2FHonours%2Fcarling_cup_winners_2008.jpg&h=0b11c714&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwS3332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwS3332.jpg&h=f8214e0d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7O2vxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7O2vxd.jpg&h=766aa625&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(部份圖片由淫心黃黃巴打提供)</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><ins><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">榮耀：</div></strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">甲組聯賽 冠軍：1950/1951、1960/1961<br />\n足總盃 冠軍：1900/1901、1920/1921、1960/1961、1961/1962、1966/1967、1980/1981、1981/1982、1990/1991<br />\n聯賽盃 冠軍：1970/1971、1972/1973、1998/1999、2007/2008<br />\n歐洲盃賽冠軍盃 冠軍：1962/1963<br />\n歐洲足協杯 冠軍：1971/1972、1983/1984<br />\n</div>"}]}